# Starship Configuration Standards

## Custom Module Fix

**Critical**: Use `$custom` not `$custom.module-name` in format strings.

`$custom.aws_sso` renders as `$custom` + literal `.aws_sso` text.

```toml
# ❌ Wrong
format = "$all\$custom.aws_sso\$line_break\$character"

# ✅ Correct
format = "$all\$custom\$line_break\$character"
```

## Standards

- **Cloud modules**: Only show when active, colorize values only
- **Helpers**: Place in `zsh/.zsh/bin/` for stowing
- **General**: Use `add_newline = false`, avoid `$fill`
